aware of the following:<o:p></o:p></p>

<ul>
<b>Data Accuracy:</b> Weather data, particularly
from personal stations, can be subject to inaccuracies, equipment malfunctions,
sensor errors, environmental factors, or transmission issues. Forecasts are
inherently uncertain and may change rapidly.<o:p></o:p></p>

<b>Not for Critical Decisions:</b> The
information presented on this website is for <b>informational and entertainment
purposes only</b>. It should <b>not</b> be used for making critical decisions where personal safety, property, or financial well-being
could be impacted. This includes, but is not limited to, decisions related to
travel, aviation, marine activities, agricultural operations, emergency
preparedness, or any activity requiring precise and verified meteorological
data.<o:p></o:p></p>

<b>Official Sources:</b> For critical weather
information, warnings, and advisories, always consult official governmental
weather sources (e.g., National Weather Service, local meteorological
agencies). These organizations provide verified and authoritative weather data
and alerts.<o:p></o:p></p>

<b>No Guarantees:</b> We make no warranties or
guarantees, express or implied, regarding the accuracy, completeness,
reliability, suitability, or timeliness of the weather information presented
herein.<o:p></o:p></p>

<b>Limitation of Liability:</b> By using this
